(firstQuint)Cancer of the Upper Aero-digestive Tract and Socio-professional Future.

 Socio-professional, medical, psychological, demographic, economic, and educational data collection in patients within the care pathway of upper aero-digestive tract cancer.

 A series of questionnaires will be presented at the initial consultation and then at 6 months, at 12 months and at 18 months during follow-up visits.

 Medical data will be collected via the CRF.

